snippet.title: Omitted | Full Game Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Omitted is an psychological indie horror game. Discover the secrects of an old creepy hospital.

My PC specs
▪️ GPU: Asus Dual RTX 3060TI 6GB OC ▪️ Motherboard: Asrock B550 Phantom Gaming 4 ▪️ CPU: AMD Ryzen 5 5600X @ 3.70GHz (4.60GHz) ▪️ CPU cooler: SilentiumPC Fera 3 ▪️ Case: SilentiumPC AR6 TG ▪️ RAM: Kingston HyperX 32GB (2x8GB) DDR4 @ 3200MHz ▪️ SSD1: WD Blue SN550 500Gt M.2 NVMe SSD ▪️ SSD2: Crucial MX500 1 TB SATA III SSD 2,5 ▪️ PSU: SilentiumPC Supremo 650W, 80 Plus Gold ▪️ Operating system: Windows 11

My PC accessories
▪️ Mouse: Logitech G502 HERO (Wired)
▪️ Monitor1: Lenovo G27q-20
▪️ Monitor 2: LG 27UL650-W
▪️ Headset: HyperX Cloud II (Wired)
▪️ Keyboard: Roccat suora

Gameplay recorded with OBS in 2k resolution.
